```bash
node .claude/skills/omega-cursor-cli/scripts/ask-cursor.mjs "PROMPT" [--model MODEL] [--json] [--sandbox] [--timeout-ms N]
```

- `--json` maps to `cursor-agent --output-format json`.
- `--sandbox` maps to `cursor-agent --force`.